name: Prison Identities - Elizabeth Harvey
description:
Prison Identities - Elizabeth Harvey,  a convicted female prisoner with no mug shot. There are records of Elizabeth and her crimes, accompanied by a rough description of features, for example, large eyes, scars above eyes. 

This is part of the Prison Residencies project at Shepton Mallet Prison, UK 18/09/2021 - 03/10/2021. This collage uses real records of female prisoners from the UK Victorian era. The facial image is completely made up only influenced by the historical records.
